OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine in
OL,7,Fplaces. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be dry and rather cloudy.
OL,9,FFreshening westerly breeze later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FMainly dry and cloudy, chance
OL,12,Fof a light shower at first. Becoming
OL,13,Fsomewhat brighter in the afternoon.
OL,14,FFurther patchy light rain spreads
OL,15,Fsoutheast in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
